cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with visualizing and refining the invariances of learned representations in image classification networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with geometric image transformations, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
